1
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:25,600
Well...

2
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:29,800
Those people are just talking nonsense.

3
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:31,440
Don't take it to heart.

4
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,480
Yes, Inspector.

5
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:33,800
You must not easily believe

6
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:34,720
their absurd claims.

7
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:55,040
Inspector!

8
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:56,240
Somebody, come quickly!

9
00:01:56,240 --> 00:01:56,800
Call a doctor!

10
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:02,040
Fellow townsfolk,

11
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,120
please gather around!

12
00:02:03,440 --> 00:02:04,360
Fellow townsfolk,

13
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:06,400
my lady has something to say.

14
00:02:06,880 --> 00:02:08,240
Please gather around!

15
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:11,680
Look,

16
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:12,800
this little girl's eyes

17
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:14,160
are actually blue.

18
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:14,680
Yeah.

19
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,680
I've never seen

20
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:16,240
a little girl like this.

21
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:17,800
She must be a master.

22
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,240
I believe you all know

23
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:21,240
about the once-powerful

24
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,320
Marshal Huang's family,

25
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:24,400
and the two recent murders.

26
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,400
But you surely don't know

27
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:31,040
that a year ago,

28
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:32,800
Marshal Huang sent people across Jiangyu City

29
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,160
for a massive manhunt.

30
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:36,600
It was actually because his wife, Su Yao,

31
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:38,680
just like Marshal Huang,

32
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,600
died a tragic death.

33
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:41,680
Oh my god!

34
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:42,760
So that's what happened.

35
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:43,600
No wonder.

36
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:44,800
I felt at the time

37
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,760
like they were looking for someone.

38
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:46,760
Now it seems

39
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:48,040
they were looking for the killer

40
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:48,600
of the Marshal's wife.

41
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:49,400
No.

42
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:51,680
These three deaths were not caused by man,

43
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,400
but are heaven's

44
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:55,800
punishment upon Huang Zhenyue's family.

45
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:01,880
Don't doubt it.

46
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:03,160
My lady

47
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:04,400
was born with Clairvoyance.

48
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:05,880
She can observe the heavens above

49
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,240
and the underworld below.

50
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,520
She can also predict the future.

51
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,320
Her readings are always spot on

52
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:11,480
and very accurate.

53
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:12,880
Then what exactly happened?

54
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:14,080
Tell us quickly!

55
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:15,360
Tell us!

56
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:16,160
Tell us!

57
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:17,560
That Huang Zhenyue

58
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:19,480
ruled Jiangyu City with an iron fist

59
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:20,320
and committed countless murders.

60
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,560
How could such evil deeds

61
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:24,080
escape the eyes of heaven?

62
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:25,840
That's why it brought about punishment.

63
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:27,200
Someone said before

64
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:28,840
that the Marshal's death was retribution.

65
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:30,160
It seems it's really true.

66
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:32,440
The cycle of karma in this world

67
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:34,000
is not something you mortals

68
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,080
can easily see through.

69
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,320
Huang Zhenyue's sins

70
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:39,280
have long been secretly

71
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,320
recorded in the books.

72
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:42,040
Now it's just retribution.

73
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:09,600
Don't run!

74
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:11,000
Don't run!

75
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:12,160
Don't run!

76
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:13,080
Don't run!

77
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:15,840
I won't leave.

78
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,760
I'll stay here with you.

79
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,480
I will definitely find you.

80
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:54,600
You must get well soon.

81
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,040
Qingqing.

82
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:10,560
Chun Cheng.

83
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:12,160
How is the Inspector doing?

84
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:14,880
Much better.

85
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,440
His fever has broken.

86
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,000
It's just that his body

87
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:19,520
is still very weak.

88
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,640
Rumors are flying around the city right now.

89
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,080
They're all saying that Marshal Huang,

90
00:05:25,400 --> 00:05:25,960
President Huang,

91
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,480
and the death of the Inspector's mother

92
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:28,960
are all because the Marshal

93
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:30,400
killed too many people when he was alive,

94
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:31,960
which brought down heaven's punishment.

95
00:05:32,080 --> 00:05:33,200
That's outrageous!

96
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:34,760
How could they spout such

97
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:35,640
nonsense?

98
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:41,600
Jinrong!

99
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:42,640
Inspector!

100
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:44,640
Slow down.

101
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:46,720
Have a seat.

102
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:47,480
Have a seat.

103
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:49,720
Why did you fall?

104
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:50,720
I'm fine.

105
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,640
I just wanted a sip of water.

106
00:05:52,960 --> 00:05:53,480
But...

107
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:54,960
Your fever just broke.

108
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,520
Your body is still weak.

109
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:57,640
If you want water,

110
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:59,040
just tell me.

111
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:00,840
I'll pour you another glass.

112
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:03,520
Qingqing.

113
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:05,280
While I was sick,

114
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:06,880
you've been taking care of me.

115
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:07,960
Thank you.

116
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:18,280
Inspector.

117
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:20,400
The autopsy results are out.

118
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:22,840
The victim, Huang Changsheng,

119
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:24,520
died of the same cause as the Marshal.

120
00:06:24,840 --> 00:06:26,280
Both had their breathing blocked by an external force,

121
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,200
and died of suffocation.

122
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:34,880
As for the case's progress right now,

123
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,400
we don't have a single clue.

124
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:37,840
What should we do?

125
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:45,480
Come with me to find someone.

126
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,280
Let's go see.

127
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:51,480
Top-quality milk!

128
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:53,600
Why did you bring me here?

129
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,760
To find my mother's old personal servant.

130
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:57,840
After my mother passed away,

131
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,760
the servants all scattered.

132
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:02,160
Only Ba Gu stayed here,

133
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,080
running a porridge stall for a living.

134
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,080
So I want to ask her

135
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,040
and see

136
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:08,160
if there are any clues.

137
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:21,520
Ba Gu.

138
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:23,960
Young Master.

139
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:25,320
Why are you here?

140
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,480
Come, have a seat.

141
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:31,080
Ba Gu.

142
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:32,400
How have you been lately?

143
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:34,080
I was doing okay before.

144
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,320
But these past few days,

145
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:36,840
not so well.

146
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:40,200
Young Master.

147
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,400
I heard about the Marshal.

148
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,520
Don't be too sad,

149
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:46,080
or you'll ruin your health.

150
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:50,400
Ba Gu.

151
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:51,960
Actually, I came this time

152
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:52,960
to ask you something.

153
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:54,640
You said my mother

154
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:56,480
met someone a few days before she died.

155
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:57,960
But

156
00:07:58,520 --> 00:07:59,280
I haven't been able to find

157
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:00,200
any clues about this person.

158
00:08:00,840 --> 00:08:02,040
Could you think carefully?

159
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:02,640
Did this person

160
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:04,080
have any specific features?

161
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,080
That person came at night.

162
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:09,600
They stood far outside.

163
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:11,960
It was too dark,

164
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:13,080
so I couldn't see clearly.

165
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:17,080
But judging by the figure,

166
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:18,720
it should be a man.

167
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:20,840
A man?

168
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:26,080
Sorceress Youtong

169
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:27,600
will break the Huang family's evil curse

170
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:28,840
and keep everyone safe!

171
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:30,600
Sorceress Youtong!

172
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:37,840
Sorceress Youtong!

173
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,040
Break the evil curse!

174
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,200
Keep everyone safe!

175
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:54,640
Seems pretty impressive.

176
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:56,040
Fellow townsfolk,

177
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:57,760
The Huang family's sins are grave,

178
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,160
bringing disaster to Jiangyu City.

179
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,640
Sorceress Youtong,

180
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:01,720
for the sake of the people,

181
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,160
has specially prayed to the founder

182
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:04,520
for blessings.

183
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:05,520
Everyone,

184
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:06,840
if you wish to stay safe,

185
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,640
you must take a peace amulet

186
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:09,320
to be protected.

187
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,400
Sorceress Youtong?

188
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:13,040
Never heard of her.

189
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,200
Give me one!

190
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:16,840
Please calm down, everyone.

191
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:17,520
One at a time.

192
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,200
Sorceress Youtong

193
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:20,280
will keep you all safe.

194
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,400
This is absolute nonsense!

195
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:23,640
She's deceiving the public with lies!

196
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:24,520
Qingqing.

197
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:25,400
Don't hold me back!

198
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:25,960
Qingqing.

199
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:27,760
Right now, our family

200
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,280
is at the center of a storm.

201
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:30,600
If right now

202
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:31,880
we clash with them,

203
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,960
it will only invite more rumors.

204
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,480
It won't help our investigation.

205
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:37,720
Don't rush!

206
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:38,320
Line up!

207
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,000
The case takes priority.

208
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,120
Give me one!

209
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:42,720
Don't push!

210
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,560
Give it to me first!

211
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,080
Sorceress!

212
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:47,080
One person at a time!

213
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:47,840
There's enough for everyone!

214
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:48,720
I beg for one!

215
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:49,440
Okay, okay, okay.

216
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:50,480
Thank you, Sorceress!

217
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,560
Thank you, Sorceress!

218
00:09:52,560 --> 00:09:53,840
Thank you, thank you!

219
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:54,600
Okay, okay.

220
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:03,200
Young Master!

221
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,120
Inspector!

222
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,560
You're finally back!

223
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:08,680
What's wrong?
